{"tid":651690,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"{EXCEL} JJ插法救教","createTime":"2018-05-03T09:25:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T12:07:04.000Z","uid":78186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"14c23d800fede01c0eef74df5e7e3cb57e298ae3","tid":651690,"uid":78186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:25:06.000Z","msg":"我想係一個儲存格入面揾一組8字頭數字, 8位, eg. 8XXXXXXX<br />\n<br />\n但係佢冇任何RULES, RANDOM 出現既, 有無一條FORMULA可以搵到?<br />\n<br />\nEG<br />\n51689153 XHipper - REG SC 50g fr WR ML 18ml + WR Essence 2ml x4 (82279465)<br />\n99990382 YU 750+500  - shipper 82246902<br />\n<br />\n唔想一個一個咁打<br />\n<br />\n之前揾人幫手整個一次<br />\n<br />\n條FORMULA係咁, 當時搵9字CODE, 搵到的, 但改成&gt;80000000, 就唔得了<br />\n<br />\n=IFERROR(INT(MID(B1387,MATCH(TRUE,--MID(B1387,ROW(INDIRECT(&quot;1:&quot;&amp;LEN(B1387)-7)),8)&gt;90000000,0),8)),&quot;&quot;)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc6b07ece2323d02ff4b28a98271093f3390e9e","tid":651690,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:42:38.000Z","msg":"用vba就好易搞掂"},{"pid":"01e4c89f3ad740f6c6eb80a5fe9f3d8d451aface","tid":651690,"uid":78186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcc6b07ece2323d02ff4b28a98271093f3390e9e","tid":651690,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:42:38.000Z","msg":"用vba就好易搞掂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:46:42.000Z","msg":"大師可否指點迷津"},{"pid":"572e45ae4767b425a2645610bb23d7556e49502e","tid":651690,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcc6b07ece2323d02ff4b28a98271093f3390e9e","tid":651690,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:42:38.000Z